The paper discusses the practical implementation and comparison of training and sampling schemes for recurrent neural networks in various applications such as text, speech, and image processing. This suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE), and Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV).
